Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:11.28,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,618.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:15.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:18.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:23.00,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:26.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:30.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:33.59,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:36.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:40.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:44.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:48.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:50.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:54.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:00:59.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:02.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.71,0:01:11.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:15.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:18.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx90\fs105\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,150.389)}The Monstrous Poison Flower Bararanga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,690.389)}Secret of the Terror House
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.27,0:01:31.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Having received word from\Na member of the Rider Kid Corps
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:35.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,that Shocker combatants were\Nspotted in a Tokyo suburb,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:38.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Taki Kazuya was racing to the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wretched Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't realize that we intentionally\Nlet the Rider Kid Corps see us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to lure him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see what he gets...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A Shocker cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A Shocker monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to let them know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Koichi, the pigeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope my pigeon makes\Nit back to HQ safely...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.59,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs50}Kamen Rider Kid Corps Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we have a pigeon in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Koichi's pigeon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no message attached...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I found this in its wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Smells nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman! Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops! Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He collapsed after smelling the thorn\NI found in the messenger pigeon's wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:45.64,Italics,,0,0,0,,A thorn from a rose...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Awakened, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rose Estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose Estate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You were collapsed in the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you here to let you rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about all the trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You must rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I need to get back.\NMy comrades will worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But, we were just getting\Nto know each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come back again to\Ngive a more proper thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you take this\Nrose, to remember me by?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lovely rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I am very proud of my roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a very fine smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of that rose,\Nthe way she was acting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very rude of you to enter\Nmy room without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't shown reflected in that mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You caught on, did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki Kazuya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent work, Bararanga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use him against Hongo and his allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Be on your guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's found us and\Nthey're on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of these roses...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've shown yourself, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! Come down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:54.77,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it. It's a powerful tranquilizer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When it enters the human\Nbody, it addles the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Damned Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Chairman. You're feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, that was something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He said there was a powerful\Npoison in that thorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Naoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing out of the ordinary for now? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you find anything, contact us at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! We will!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little worried about Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to visit Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Choco.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you're eating\Nwhile Mr. Taki's missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ever not working\Nthat mouth of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really beside myself\Nwith worry right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking kind of pale...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah...\N- You're acting so weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki and the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to their hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out, Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear the way, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Bararanga must have gotten to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them into the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You made it back safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?\NWe've been worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They got to you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Remove the boys' roses, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember anything after\Nshe attacked me in the Rose Estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:16:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The poison in those roses addled\Nthe minds of you and the boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm going back to the Rose Estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman, they used me\Nto attack you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let this stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I get how you feel,\Nbut you need to calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides... she doesn't\Nknow I've recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can pretend to still\Nbe under her control,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and infiltrate Shocker's base.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there nothing I can say to stop you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Just a minute, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an antidote I\Ndesigned for the rose poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Inject it and the roses' smell\Nwon't affect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good. Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:17:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But it only helps with the smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't survive a prick from the thorns.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Inject us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What, were you listening in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We have our own pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to help Mr. Taki, and restore\Nthe honor of the Rider Kid Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, just don't forget to\Ncontact me if things go south.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. If I'm not back in thirty\Nminutes, contact Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you've returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you dispose of Hongo and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. You've done well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're truly one of us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell, the plan was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki is now one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's truly worth celebrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You are henceforth a member of Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not trust that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You betrayed me, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot let a traitor\Nleave this place alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Taki is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:56.15,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:59.28,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:03.24,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:06.82,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:10.41,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:14.00,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:16.58,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:20.17,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:24.88,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:28.39,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:39.06,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:41.90,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:46.24,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:49.83,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:53.41,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:56.75,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:21:59.75,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:03.26,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:07.89,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.89,0:22:11.39,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:22.40,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:25.28,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:29.49,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:32.95,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.95,0:22:36.71,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:39.92,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:42.96,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:46.80,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:51.30,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:54.93,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Screw Block!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:59.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The terrible flower monster\NBararanga was defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:02.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker wasn't about to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.82,0:23:06.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi and Taki\NKazuya's fight was far from over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.03,0:23:08.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fight on, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:10.72,Cont,,0,60,160,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:12.91,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(307.175,272.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:15.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I am the monstrous Seadragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.99,0:23:19.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I'll use the 8,300 volts that\Nflow through my body
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.21,0:23:21.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to put an end to the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:25.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,My brothers Seadragon II\Nand III will appear as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:27.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Stay tuned to this channel next week
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:30.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,for "Three Electric\NMonsters: the Seadragons!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:30.93,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy80\fs115\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(507.167,710.389)}Three Electric Monsters: \Nthe Seadragons!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:50.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.28,0:23:57.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.79,0:24:01.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.54,0:24:05.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.21,0:24:08.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.88,0:24:12.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Poison Flower Bararanga\NSecret of the Terror House